snippet.title: Redmatch 2 Trailer (2020)
snippet.description:
A free fast-paced multiplayer shooter, with customizable death effects, skins, healthbars, game modifiers, and tons of unique maps to play on. Use resource packs to change the entire look of the game.

Play the game! https://store.steampowered.com/app/1280770/Redmatch_2/
Support me on Patreon! https://www.patreon.com/rugbug

To everyone who followed the game and helped playtest and give feedback during its development, thank you. If you want to join the community, you can join our discord server at https://rugbug.net/discord

Music by Otis McDonald
